/////////////////////////////////

Run the project normall as describe in the handout.

To compile, use:
$ make

To run the LICM (loop invariant code motion) pass, use:
$ opt -load ./loop-invariant-code-motion.so -loop-simplify -cd-licm test.bc -o out.bc

To run the DCE (dead come elimination) pass, use:
$ opt -load ./dead-code-elimination.so -cd-dce test.bc -o out.bc

/////////////////////////////////

A breakdown of the relevant variables at each program point between blocks is
written to STDERR in a readable format.
